#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.cumsum.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.cumsum"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:1 of
msgid "Return the cumulative sum of the elements along a given axis."
msgstr "沿给定轴返回元素的累积和。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:3 of
msgid "Input tensor."
msgstr "输入张量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:5 of
msgid ""
"Axis along which the cumulative sum is computed. The default (None) is to"
" compute the cumsum over the flattened tensor."
msgstr "计算累积和的轴。默认值（None）是对展平后的张量进行计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:8 of
msgid ""
"Type of the returned tensor and of the accumulator in which the elements "
"are summed.  If `dtype` is not specified, it defaults to the dtype of "
"`a`, unless `a` has an integer dtype with a precision less than that of "
"the default platform integer.  In that case, the default platform integer"
" is used."
msgstr ""
"返回张量和累加器的类型，其中元素被求和。如果未指定 `dtype`，则默认为 `a` "
"的数据类型，除非 `a` 具有精度低于默认平台整数的整数类型。在这种情况下，"
"使用默认平台整数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:14 of
msgid ""
"Alternative output tensor in which to place the result. It must have the "
"same shape and buffer length as the expected output but the type will be "
"cast if necessary. See `doc.ufuncs` (Section \"Output arguments\") for "
"more details."
msgstr ""
"用于放置结果的替代输出张量。它必须具有与预期输出相同的形状和缓冲区长度，"
"但必要时类型会被转换。详见 `doc.ufuncs`（“输出参数”部分）获取更多细节。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:20 of
msgid ""
"**cumsum_along_axis** -- A new tensor holding the result is returned "
"unless `out` is specified, in which case a reference to `out` is "
"returned. The result has the same size as `a`, and the same shape as `a` "
"if `axis` is not None or `a` is a 1-d tensor."
msgstr ""
"**cumsum_along_axis** —— 除非指定了 `out`，否则返回一个保存结果的新张量；"
"若指定了 `out`，则返回对 `out` 的引用。结果与 `a` 大小相同，且当 `axis` "
"不为 None 或 `a` 为一维张量时，形状也相同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:28 of
msgid ":py:obj:`sum`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:29 of
msgid "Sum tensor elements."
msgstr "对张量元素求和。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:31 of
msgid ":py:obj:`trapz`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:32 of
msgid "Integration of tensor values using the composite trapezoidal rule."
msgstr "使用复合梯形法则对张量值进行积分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:34 of
msgid ":py:obj:`diff`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:35 of
msgid "Calculate the n-th discrete difference along given axis."
msgstr "沿给定轴计算第 n 个离散差分。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:38 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:39 of
msgid ""
"Arithmetic is modular when using integer types, and no error is raised on"
" overflow."
msgstr "使用整数类型时，运算是模运算，溢出时不会引发错误。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.cumsum.cumsum:43 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

